item.title: Anyway to dupe NP's or items?
item.dc:creator: @ownagesbot ownagesbot
item.description:
@ownagesbot wrote:

I don’t claim to know much about Neopets but if they have small flash games where you win points then providing it sends the scores off to a server app (and doesnt just save them into a database directly) then theoretically you could:

  1. Sniff out the packets.
  2. Figure out packet structures.
  3. Figure out/decrypt any encryption. (If any)
  4. Modify the packet.
  5. Re-encrypt if nessarcerry.

My spelling is apauling, but thats the general idea anyway.

Art Money and co. are only memory editors, therefore they only modify code thats in your computers memory. Thus most shit is client side. However, if the client sends crutial information regarding scores off to the server, and the server just accepts what the client sends it, then theoretically theres no need for packet modification, just modify the score thats in memory and the client will send that off.

But like I said, this is theory and I have no idea how neopets actually works.

It’s not encrypted flash

It’s possible to decrypt and encrypt Neopets scores, just trace the code. It took me about 3 days (And that was because I was stubborn and wanted to decrypt my own scores…hint: you don’t have to.) item.title: Anyway to dupe NP's or items?
item.dc:creator: @arrowster arrowster
item.description:
@arrowster wrote:

No offense, but I think some of you guys are the stupidest people on earth.

  1. You CAN’T hack neopets with cheat engine/art money. They are just used for the flash games, you can change the money in your bank using art money but it’s just what you see not what it really is.
  2. WTF, are you guys so stupid that you don’t know how to make a cheat table for a game. I can make one blind folded(no seriously im a touch typer, but the seeing the variables after I click enter would be a problem). I mean all you need to do is A)choose your application. B)search for the value of the variable you wish to change. C)Change the variable in the program, search again D)Repeat B-C untill theres 1 or 2 variables left E)Add the variables that are there at the end. F) Then just save it as a cheat table, edit values to what you want. I mean it’s so easy a caveman could do it.

I Just use cheats for games. I found one for Bullseye Shootout (with the turtle guy) where it like automatically hits the center of the target, so you get like MAJOR NPs. Do that like make a file name it NeoPets Game Cheats and put in cheats for all the popular games, so when a game that you have a hack/cheat for is featured, then you use the cheat and ge the extra NPS.
